          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The present method of measuring the Be-9 photoneutron",
                " cross section using radioactive sources  Y-89  (1.85",
                " MeV)   and   Sb-124   (1.69   MeV)   is  capable  of",
                " considerably  higher   precision   than   techniques",
                " previously used."
              ]
